description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by psychological astrologer Dr. Jen Freed to read the birth charts of our callers in order to help guide them on their sex & relationship journey – & this is only part one, so be on the lookout for part two! 

Emily & Dr. Jen talk to listeners just like you to help them with their sexual journeys based off of the exact time, place & date they were born. Some of the advice given includes how to navigate new relationships, ways to masturbate better & body image.


If you like the show, please let us know and we can have more call in shows like this. Email feedback@sexwithemily.com or leave us a comment on iTunes or wherever you listen to the show!


Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For even more sex talk, tips, & tricks visit sexwithemily.com
